The article is about President Donald J. Trump's criteria for selecting a new Justice for the Supreme Court. Trump emphasizes the importance of impeccable credentials, great intellect, unbiased judgement, and a deep reverence for the laws and Constitution of the United States. He also highlights his commitment to transparency by making the list of potential justices public for the American people to see and evaluate. Additionally, Trump mentions that he has consistently followed a transparent process, as seen in his selection of Justice Neil Gorsuch. Lastly, he states that he seeks justices who will faithfully interpret the Constitution as written, reflecting a principled vision for the Supreme Court.